<refsect1 id="libgtksourceview-2.0-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para><literal>&cmd;</literal> provides extensions to the GTK+ text control
to support syntax highlighting and other features useful for source code editors.
<literal>&cmd;</literal> makes use of language specification files in XML format
to define how to highlight syntax for each language.</para>
<para>To access the API documentation, you must install the developer version
of the package.</para>
</refsect1>
